description.fr: {CharacterName:708} est missionné par {CharacterName:474} pour retourner dans les galeries à la recherche de la {Summoning:1354}. Resté sur le carreau, {CharacterName:654} boude un peu...
description.en: {CharacterName:474} has sent {CharacterName:708} back to the tunnels in search of the {Summoning:1354}. Left behind, {CharacterName:654} is pouting a bit…
description.es: {CharacterName:474} le ha encargado a {CharacterName:708} la misión de volver a las galerías en busca de la {Summoning:1354}. Al quedarse al margen, {CharacterName:654} se enfurruña un poco…
description.de: {CharacterName:708} wurde von {CharacterName:474} damit beauftragt, in den Tunneln erneut nach der {Summoning:1354} zu suchen. {CharacterName:654} schmollt ein bisschen, da er zurückbleiben muss\_...
description.pt: {CharacterName:708} recebeu de {CharacterName:474} a missão de voltar às galerias e procurar a {Summoning:1354}. {CharacterName:654} não gostou muito de ter sido deixado de fora…

descriptionFinished.fr: Suite au tremblement d'{WorldZone:208[Astrub]}, les galeries souterraines sont complètement encombrées. {CharacterName:708} doit d'abord dégager les accès avant de pouvoir s'y aventurer.
descriptionFinished.en: An earthquake in {WorldZone:208[Astrub]} has left the underground tunnels completely blocked. {CharacterName:708} must clear the way before he can go back in.
descriptionFinished.es: Debido al temblor de {WorldZone:208[Astrub]}, las galerías subterráneas han quedado completamente obstruidas. {CharacterName:708} primero tiene que despejar los accesos antes de poder aventurarse en ellas.
descriptionFinished.de: Nach dem Erdbeben in {WorldZone:208[Astrub]} sind die unterirdischen Tunnel komplett eingestürzt. {CharacterName:708} muss zuerst den Weg freiräumen, bevor er hineingelangen kann.
descriptionFinished.pt: Após o tremor de {WorldZone:208[Astrub]}, as galerias subterrâneas ficaram completamente entulhadas. Agora, {CharacterName:708} precisa limpar as entradas antes de poder se aventurar por lá.
